    public interface IKML
extends IFeature<IGeoRenderable>, IGeoDocument

    • Method Detail

      • getFeatureList

        java.util.List<IFeature> getFeatureList()
        This method retrieves the list of feature generated from the KML document. This method is for internal use only. Client software manipulating the list or the features listed, will cause unforeseen results.
        Returns:
        The list of features.

      • getImageLayerList

        java.util.List<IImageLayer> getImageLayerList()
        This method retrieves the list of image layers generated from the ground overlays in the KML document. This method is for internal use only. Client software manipulating the list or the image layers listed, will cause unforeseen results.
        Returns:
        The list of image layers.

      • findKMLId

        java.util.List<IFeature> findKMLId(java.lang.String kmlId)
        This method retrieves a list of features which are generated from a KML placemark with the specified KML id.
        Parameters:
        kmlId - The placemark Id.
        Returns:
        The list of features with the specified KML id.

      • exportToKML

        java.lang.String exportToKML()
        This method retrieves a KML string representing all contained features and image layers. It is important to understand that the string returned is a valid KML document, but may not match the initial document.
        Returns:
